	<h1 class="posttitle"><a href="http://theredspoonblog.com/2012/04/17/heaven-on-a-spoon/" title="Permanent Link to coffee ice cream with baileys fudge ripple">coffee ice cream with baileys fudge ripple</a></h1>
	


	<div class="article"><p><a title="first bite, just as good as the last" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/theredspoonblog/6942024452/" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackPageview','/yoast-ga/outbound-article/http://www.flickr.com']);"><img src="http://farm6.staticflickr.com/5238/6942024452_4b6df347de.jpg" alt="first bite, just as good as the last" width="500" height="334" /></a></p>
